    <item>
      <title>监管机构称，美国未能充分说明向乌克兰运送武器的情况</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/us-fails-to-fully-account-for-arms-sent-ukraine-watchdog-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[五角大楼的内部监督机构表示，美国未能完全追踪运往乌克兰用于防御俄罗斯的一些最敏感的武器和装备——但没有说任何援助被盗或滥用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/us-fails-to-fully-account-for-arms-sent-ukraine-watchdog-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 17:15:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管危机加深，布林肯仍称赞中东之行取得进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/blinken-touts-progress-on-mideast-trip-as-crisis-only-deepens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯表示，美国在中东的合作伙伴已准备好采取措施，以实现该地区的长期稳定——尽管红海的新袭击以及以色列和真主党之间的暴力表明该地区的危机只会变得更加严重。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/blinken-touts-progress-on-mideast-trip-as-crisis-only-deepens</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 16:57:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>米莱誓言“迟早”将关闭阿根廷央行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/milei-vows-to-shutter-argentina-s-central-bank-sooner-or-later</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈维尔·米莱总统自上任以来因其实用主义而赢得赞誉，他坚持其最具争议的竞选承诺之一：关闭阿根廷央行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/milei-vows-to-shutter-argentina-s-central-bank-sooner-or-later</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 16:41:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>五角大楼监察长将调查奥斯汀住院情况</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/pentagon-inspector-general-will-probe-austin-hospitalization</link>
      <description><![CDATA[五角大楼的内部监督机构宣布，将调查国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀的住院情况，此前他因前列腺手术出现并发症，但几天来没有告诉白宫。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/pentagon-inspector-general-will-probe-austin-hospitalization</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 16:19:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>胡塞武装领导人誓言将对美国的任何军事袭击做出“重大”回应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/houthi-leader-vows-big-response-to-any-us-military-assault</link>
      <description><![CDATA[也门胡塞武装领导人威胁称，如果美国及其盟友对其采取军事行动，他们将做出“重大”回应。该组织近两个月来一直在红海袭击船只。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/houthi-leader-vows-big-response-to-any-us-military-assault</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 16:00:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>五角大楼表示需要风险投资来重振国防基地</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/pentagon-says-venture-capital-needed-to-revive-defense-base</link>
      <description><![CDATA[五角大楼承认它需要注入新的想法——和风险投资——在美国寻求夺回被中国夺走的土地之际，重振其工业基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/pentagon-says-venture-capital-needed-to-revive-defense-base</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 15:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非请求联合国法院命令以色列停止对加沙的袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/south-africa-asks-un-court-to-order-israel-to-end-gaza-strikes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非呼吁联合国国际法院命令以色列结束在巴勒斯坦加沙领土上对哈马斯的战争，并裁定其军事行动构成种族灭绝。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/south-africa-asks-un-court-to-order-israel-to-end-gaza-strikes</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 12:57:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普出席爱荷华州预选会议前最后一天的欺诈审判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/trump-to-attend-last-day-of-fraud-trial-just-before-iowa-caucus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在爱荷华州共和党预选会议前四天，前总统唐纳德·特朗普在 1,000 英里外公开露面，这很容易演变成一场竞选活动：纽约州针对他的 3.7 亿美元民事欺诈案的结案陈词。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/trump-to-attend-last-day-of-fraud-trial-just-before-iowa-caucus</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈佛大学因反犹太主义“猖獗”而被犹太学生起诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/harvard-sued-by-jewish-students-citing-antisemitism-on-campus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈佛大学被犹太学生起诉，他们声称学校未能惩罚哈马斯袭击以色列后校园反犹太主义飙升，并导致总统克劳丁·盖伊下台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/harvard-sued-by-jewish-students-citing-antisemitism-on-campus</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 10:58:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>白宫支持扣押被冻结的俄罗斯资产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/white-house-throws-support-behind-seizing-frozen-russian-assets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登总统的政府正在支持一项立法，允许其扣押价值 3000 亿美元的俄罗斯冻结资产中的一部分，以帮助支付乌克兰的重建费用，这一转变是在白宫寻求获得国会支持以进一步资助针对弗拉基米尔·普京军队的战争之际发生的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/white-house-throws-support-behind-seizing-frozen-russian-assets</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 20:38:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
